di kamarmu mengobatinya.

181
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,159
Aku hanya…

182
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,080
…ingin bicara denganmu.

183
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,200
Katakanlah.

184
00:11:56,159 --> 00:11:57,039
Aku akan dengar.

185
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:05,039
Setelah kau pergi semalam,
aku menyesal.

186
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,200
Kemarin aku minum sedikit arak.

187
