Hanchen bermain air.

558
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:03,719
Jarang bisa bersantai.

559
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:09,600
Jika dipikir, beberapa hari lagi
ulang tahun Xiaojie.

560
00:38:11,439 --> 00:38:14,360
Aku sudah hampir lupa.

561
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:15,159
Jangan bahas dia.

562
00:38:17,439 --> 00:38:22,600
Aku ingat, saat Xiaojie meninggal,
aku pernah ceritakan teori teh.

563
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:25,239
Bercerita tentang lapang dada.

564
00:38:26,199 --> 00:38:28,879
Salju putih jatuh
dan mencair di atas kaki.

565
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:32,719
Angin sepoi-sepoi tiba-tiba
tak berhenti berhembus.

566
00:38:33,679 --> 00:38:36,080
Meskipun miskin,
sulit untuk berhenti makan.

567
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:39,840
Hanya bisa duduk
menikmati tanah tandus.

568
00:38:41,399 --> 00:38:43,239
Dulu, kau paling pintar
dalam teori teh.

569
00:38:43,719 --> 00:38:45,159
Kenapa sekarang kau lupa?

570
