Jika kau menjual,
maka pasti bisa dibeli.

571
00:38:47,919 --> 00:38:49,439
Congwen ingin beli tanpa tawar.

572
00:38:49,639 --> 00:38:50,919
Orang bijak harus lapang dada.

573
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:54,320
